<font size = +1>PART ONE: PICTURES</font><br>
<p>
This update is a little late coming, and its not pants' fault, its mine and I apologize.  Its been a pretty amazing week, with us finally breaking into the elemental planes.  Its 
strange, during the RZ fight I could feel it, I think everyone could feel it, almost right away.  It reminded me of our first victory against the Emporer in Ssra, at like 80% 
life I already knew we were going to win, and as his life continued to drop you could tell everyone could feel it, hearts racing, swearing in guild chat.  It was intense and 
I'd be lieing if it didn't feel... contrived.  I believe it was fate that brought us to that point.  I believe that that night held for every one of us, the very meaning of our 
lives.  This is a war, and we are soilders.  What if tomorrow, the war could be over?  Isn't that worth fighting for?  Isn't that worth dieing.... oops wrong speech<br>
<p>
I know what you're thinking... I can't believe he made a matrix joke.  Oh well, thats enough from me... <br>
