<font size = +1>PART ONE: PICTURES</font><br>
<p>
Hammer here, and its been a very exciting week.  After spending quite a bit of time working on the Rallos Zek script, the only thing between us and the elemental 
planes, we finally got to the "fake" RZ:<br>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/fakeRZ.jpg"><br>
<p>
He fell quickly, bringing us to the warlord himself and an amazing battle.  I must say, I thought we did pretty well for out first attempt<br>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/RZTW59.jpg"><br>
<p>
I really wish I could make movies of EQ because Rallos does a crazy cool animation with his axe where he tosses it up and catches it and then swings it around.  Another mob 
that has an outstanding animation is Arlyxir in Solusek Ro's Tower<br>
<img src = "http://personal.ghguild.com/hammeron/arlyxir.jpg"><br>
<p>
The swooping attack on it is phenomenal<br>
